<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Animals</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* General Styling */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, #4ca1af);
            color: #f9f9f9;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes frameIn {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(100px);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        /* About Container */
        .about-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            animation: frameIn 1s ease-out;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .about-container h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f8d210, #ff6700);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .about-container p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 800px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Table Styling */
        table {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        table th,
        table td {
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        table thead {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            color: #fff;
        }

        table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        table img {
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        table img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-container h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .about-container p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            table img {
                width: 70px;
            }

            table th, table td {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }

         /* Footer Styling */
         footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        footer a {
            color: #f8d210;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #ff6700;
        }

        footer p {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Animals</h1>
        <p>Explore fascinating animals and learn about their unique characteristics and habitats.</p>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Image</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><img src="https://www.worldanimalprotection.ca/cdn-cgi/image/width=1280,format=auto/siteassets/shutterstock_2461984615.jpg" alt="Lion"></td>
                    <td>Lion</td>
                    <td>The king of the jungle, known for its majestic mane and powerful roar.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><img src="https://www.antarctica.gov.au/site/assets/files/67423/rs57281.1600x0.jpg" alt="Penguin"></td>
                    <td>Penguin</td>
                    <td>A flightless bird found in icy regions, famous for its waddling walk.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><img src="https://d1jyxxz9imt9yb.cloudfront.net/animal/806/meta_twitter_image/regular/WR202206_GiraffeTranslocation_012_360559_reduced.jpg"" alt="Giraffe"></td>
                    <td>Giraffe</td>
                    <td>The tallest land animal, known for its long neck and unique spots.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><img src="https://i.natgeofe.com/n/548467d8-c5f1-4551-9f58-6817a8d2c45e/NationalGeographic_2572187_2x1.jpg" alt="Cat"></td>
                    <td>Cat</td>
                    <td>A small, domesticated animal loved for its playful and curious nature.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0103/3784/5303/files/Dog_ageing_puppy1jpg.jpg?v=1581589639" alt="Dog"></td>
                    <td>Dog</td>
                    <td>A loyal companion and often called a human's best friend.</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 ZooManager System. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</html>
